01:16:48,744 --> 01:16:50,652
I thought something happened to you.

510
01:16:51,080 --> 01:16:52,852
I just texted you an address.

511
01:16:53,259 --> 01:16:56,417
Laura? I... I can't hear you.
You're breaking up.

512
01:17:01,348 --> 01:17:02,703
Tyler?

513
01:17:06,582 --> 01:17:09,355
Are you sure you don't want me to
take you to a hospital?

514
01:17:11,232 --> 01:17:14,057
Take me to the factory.

515
01:17:56,175 --> 01:18:00,262
- I still think we can beat this.
- Shut up, man.

516
01:18:01,387 --> 01:18:02,940
Seriously.

517
01:18:04,223 --> 01:18:06,996
You have no idea what we're dealing with.

518
01:18:09,050 --> 01:18:12,125
- I do. I saw where we're headed.
- Shut up, Kobe!

519
01:18:12,125 --> 01:18:13,522
- I saw it.
- Shut up!

520
01:18:13,522 --> 01:18:16,389
