522
01:18:27,586 --> 01:18:29,056
Stay in the car.

523
01:19:58,004 --> 01:19:59,151
Mom.

524
01:20:00,558 --> 01:20:03,947
Laura, where have you been?
I can't reach you.

525
01:20:04,791 --> 01:20:06,355
Mom, are you okay?

526
01:20:06,417 --> 01:20:08,513
I'm seeing things, Laura.

527
01:20:08,628 --> 01:20:10,546
I keep seeing that girl.

528
01:20:10,577 --> 01:20:14,404
I'm sorry... it's my fault.

529
01:20:14,570 --> 01:20:16,748
What's happening to us?

530
01:20:17,562 --> 01:20:20,304
Listen to me. I'm not going to let
anything happen to you.

531
01:20:20,627 --> 01:20:24,901
I'm going to sort this out, somehow.
I'm going to stop it, somehow.

532
01:20:25,871 --> 01:20:27,018
Mom?

533
01:20:27,904 --> 01:20:30,740
- Mom! Mom!
- I'll protect you.

534
01:20:33,888 --> 01:20:35,202
Mom!

535
01:20:39,361 --> 01:20:40,393
Mom!

536
01:20:42,186 --> 01:20:43,333
Mom!

537
01:21:01,556 --> 01:21:02,693
Laura!

538
01:21:04,382 --> 01:21:05,737
Laura!

539
01:21:07,113 --> 01:21:08,260
Tyler.

540
01:21:11,221 --> 01:21:12,368
Tyler.

541
01:21:21,928 --> 01:21:23,815
I was so worried about you.

542
01:21:26,003 --> 01:21:27,891
Laura, hey.

543
01:21:28,370 --> 01:21:30,591
Laura, look at me.

544
01:21:32,509 --> 01:21:37,201
- My mom, she's...
- Jesus, what happened to you?

545
01:21:49,377 --> 01:21:50,482
Hi.

546
01:23:15,751 --> 01:23:17,585
What do you want from me?

547
01:23:22,902 --> 01:23:25,331
What else do you want from me?

548
01:24:08,440 --> 01:24:11,046
I just want to be friends, Laura.

549
01:24:13,225 --> 01:24:15,206
Best friends.

550
01:24:19,283 --> 01:24:20,846
Forever.

551
01:24:54,217 --> 01:24:55,458
Laura.

552
01:24:57,908 --> 01:24:59,148
Laura.

553
01:25:03,527 --> 01:25:05,717
Come to me.

